overview.en: SealSC is a middleware cloud platform that links the Internet and blockchain networks and provides Oracle services through its own public chain. The aim is to enable users/enterprises to build DApps without barriers, interoperate with current public chains, and realize business scenarios such as cross-chain convergence, value circulation and data exchange.
overview.zh: SealSC是链接互联网和区块链网络的中间件云平台，并通过自有公链提供Oracle服务。旨在实现让用户/企业无门槛搭建DApp，互通目前各大公链，实现跨链融合、价值流通和数据交换等业务场景。
